comments: Johnson (BKN) initiates contact with McCollum's (POR) front that affects his SQBR along the sideline.
Green (BKN) and Covington (POR) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Green (BKN) has a grasp of Kanter's (POR) right arm and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Green (BKN) is already in Jones Jr.'s (POR) path and incidental knee-to-knee contact occurs as the switch takes place.
Kanter (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in Johnson's (BKN) path and does not deliver the contact as Johnson goes under.
Harris (BKN) is moving toward Kanter (POR) and marginal body contact occurs as they each attempt to establish rebounding position.
Kanter (POR) and Green (BKN) make incidental body contact with one another as they each attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Jones Jr.'s (POR) path and extends his hands forward as he braces for the impending contact with Jones Jr., which he absorbs.
Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Jones Jr.'s (POR) path and absorbs the contact.
Harden (BKN) goes to, not through, Jones Jr.'s (POR) space and spins off of the contact made near the lane line.

Jones Jr. (POR) maintains a rested hand on Harden's (BKN) side and marginal contact occurs after Harden's gather. Jones Jr.'s right arm comes down thereafter and marginal contact occurs with Harden's right arm during the driving shot attempt.
Kanter (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in Harden's (BKN) path and absorbs the contact. Kanter and Harden then engage and disengage with one another as the pick expires.
Harden (BKN) rests his hands on Kanter's (POR) back and marginal contact occurs as they each attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Claxton (BKN) brings his left hand to Kanter's (POR) left shoulder and marginal contact occurs as the ball is batted overhead.
Kanter (POR) moves forward toward Harris (BKN) and marginal body contact occurs as Harris is passing.
Jones Jr. (POR) extends his right arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Harden's (BKN) upper half as he is passing.
Jones Jr. (POR) cleanly dislodges Harden (BKN) of the ball before any incidental contact occurs.

Replay review of the foul called on Covington (POR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Covington is moving to the side of Harden (BKN) and maintains a legal guarding position as Harden extends his arm outward to initiate the marginal contact.
Harden (BKN) commits a take foul on Covington (POR).
Harden (BKN) gathers the pass on his right foot and maintains his left foot as his pivot foot before being fouled.
Hood (POR) and Harris (BKN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Jones Jr. (POR) commits a take foul on Harden (BKN).
Hood (POR) and Harris (BKN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Harden (BKN) and Jones Jr. (POR) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Hood (POR) commits a take foul on Green (BKN).
